OL,5, A DIY store has paid a customer #5,400 
OL,6, after rust from one of its products    
OL,7, stained her patio.                     
OL,9,FMiriam, who did not want her surname   
OL,10,Fused, purchased two pieces of garden   
OL,11,Ffurniture including a pergola, from    
OL,12,FRobert Dyas in July, 2023 and by       
OL,13,FSeptember a mark had appeared.         
OL,15,FThe Welwyn Garden City, resident said  
OL,16,Fthe retailer had been "amazing".       
OL,18,FRobert Dyas said it worked with the    
OL,19,FHertfordshire customer to resolve the  
OL,20,Fissue.                                 
